""""""""""""""""""""""
" Editing
""""""""""""""""""""""

" undo consistently on one key
nnoremap U <C-r>

" split line
vnoremap ,s gq
nnoremap ,s gqq

" Case Switch via Smarter MD Hotkeys Plugin
